high_descs: Turn around and stand to the let of the fridge.
Take a mug out of the cabinet to the left of the fridge.
Move to the right to stand in front of the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge for a few moments.
Turn around and go to the coffee maker.
Put the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around, and go to the cabinet to the left of the fridge.
Take the mug from the bottom cabinet, to the left of the fridge.
Go right to go to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Turn left, go forward then turn left to face the table.
Put the mug on the table, at the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug at the coffee maker.
